&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;本文经授权转载自：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;柳飘飘了吗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;ID：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;DSliupiaopiao&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;前几天飘飘才夸过《奇葩说》没堕落。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;今天就想撤回。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;最新一期《奇葩说》，证实了之前的传闻——&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;调换了节目播出的顺序。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;如此用心良苦，甚至不惜修改时间线，为的是什么？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;303&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqROvzQUmxoYicUUkIjnX0TVa1GTkDW51pELwIp8DEbOKxcYR64TCjbRqw/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5590312815338042&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqROvzQUmxoYicUUkIjnX0TVa1GTkDW51pELwIp8DEbOKxcYR64TCjbRqw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;991&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;37&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRrC2HJOcx6dGXrGFqLVlKRhQWvYVT3vWsY4S9g47zR4qc08Z3Qb8WoA/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.06784260515603799&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRrC2HJOcx6dGXrGFqLVlKRhQWvYVT3vWsY4S9g47zR4qc08Z3Qb8WoA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;737&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;37&quot; data-backw=&quot;518&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRJy0zBss0nedYznjs0EOE0gicrbxbOibAVl5SAnVFMtTGib849wM6p36yA/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRKp7HPeYMPWhgugL5X4zpApN2Aw4mBK6jVRpAMNbh99iaw5mNbaXLPhg/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;773.5234899328858&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;55.25167785234899&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRmM8mpVxx6RMasqdY8LefodofdACWVBEiaJ6GIbO0T9AXUic8hy2N6Bpg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.07115135834411385&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRJy0zBss0nedYznjs0EOE0gicrbxbOibAVl5SAnVFMtTGib849wM6p36yA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;773&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages js_insertlocalimg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.14925373134328357&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCadGbgrHNKj8R8y2szuPrQeOuYnqibus5meun41b9H9IWibN3ZE5iakB0UuERNwicNibSvr5ubUmShJww/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;268&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;先带大家快速回忆一下前情提要。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;上周第六期节目里，“美女学霸”许吉如被淘汰了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这时导师罗振宇英雄救美，把自己队伍唯一的救命机会，一张“在下不服卡”送给了许吉如。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;305&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRUc7mNfjvG7h3Th95rMgeYuDEuzEeIty0Hjw8cWEkmCIQhotB0un0RQ/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5630676084762866&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRUc7mNfjvG7h3Th95rMgeYuDEuzEeIty0Hjw8cWEkmCIQhotB0un0RQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;991&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;这卡的作用是什么呢？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;许吉如可以从已经获得胜利的蔡康永战队中挑选一位辩手单挑，输了的淘汰。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;蔡康永认为这是己方队员不必要面对的挑战，直接站起来表达抗议。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;303&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOsh0NVxkTOju589aicycDBUs4ZfIriaySMlwaedsnqNZlArUYrUNZ6msw/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5581395348837209&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOsh0NVxkTOju589aicycDBUs4ZfIriaySMlwaedsnqNZlArUYrUNZ6msw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;989&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;抗议无效。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;作为三辩的许吉如接受了这份馈赠，还挑选了对面看起来最弱（其实也很强）的一辩胡老师。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;结果，许吉如以10票败给胡老师的85票，依然被淘汰了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;306&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOhlWRXGkyWMoMPia1tInuvtG7giayvTbERiavmgxlcCIXAysuEca80CZlw/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5637651821862348&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOhlWRXGkyWMoMPia1tInuvtG7giayvTbERiavmgxlcCIXAysuEca80CZlw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;988&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;到这里，虽然没有赛出风度，但一切也还算正常。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;然而节目结尾，出现了类似于《创造101》的打榜体系，为淘汰选手投票，票数最高的选手就能复活。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;谁先淘汰，谁的投票通道就先开启，许吉如明显遥遥领先。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;277&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRTX0ZrCza3EUP1dUuqDVRYy6ub2bShTKibL3NnAls9ySv7x2JRJXrkQw/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5105708245243129&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRTX0ZrCza3EUP1dUuqDVRYy6ub2bShTKibL3NnAls9ySv7x2JRJXrkQw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;946&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但上周杨奇函在微博表示，自己其实比许吉如先被淘汰。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;第七期也证实了这一点，（按理说已经被淘汰的）许吉如，出现在了舞台上。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;301&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqR67dtibiaPvfMnTvJUYfiaFss2zYlS99jl605g8dZiastO2zKzCoQvV9bAg/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRNINT3kmUbGXIia4eibMOw8mwO2UXhXJhwibwriczLcIqO8oJrShWboILFg/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;984&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;546.8571428571428&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5548780487804879&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqR67dtibiaPvfMnTvJUYfiaFss2zYlS99jl605g8dZiastO2zKzCoQvV9bAg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;984&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;所以，真正的时间线是——&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;杨奇函先淘汰，许吉如后淘汰，而节目组调换了播出顺序，这样许吉如的投票通道，就等于提前了一周的时间开启。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;305&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjO0LiawNx8zOF3ibibJ89OGOs3VXolDz3IPNY0YV9Q54MFiaMicph0HuJg5icA/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5625&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjO0LiawNx8zOF3ibibJ89OGOs3VXolDz3IPNY0YV9Q54MFiaMicph0HuJg5icA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;976&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;时间线乱了，而这个票数的可信度，搞过选秀的朋友们都懂。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;你也不能说它肯定假，因为没法证实。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;你也不敢说它一定真，因为连一个以观众投票为基本逻辑的选秀比赛，都可以全盘造假。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;323&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJC2AL4WAialW80jvH9TyQQznZzuyfxCJAibyAl1g9THyR3AcIYkEDicFoDZYW6Liahx3JjCaCoXFIzS6Q/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5953125&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJC2AL4WAialW80jvH9TyQQznZzuyfxCJAibyAl1g9THyR3AcIYkEDicFoDZYW6Liahx3JjCaCoXFIzS6Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;640&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;它就像圣诞老人一样，你信，那就真的存在。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;那么，许吉如该被淘汰吗？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;许吉如该不该被骂？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;该被骂的究竟是谁？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages js_insertlocalimg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.15546218487394958&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCadGbgrHNKj8R8y2szuPrQtticOvl16AZ26Uvg82W43qKJldJsOUOqOtOsULHnqgvo1LB97cyDkBA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;238&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;首先，许吉如被淘汰，太应当了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;先看粉丝是如何为许吉如投票争议洗地的——&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;老奇葩带节奏抱团，新奇葩没出头之日。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;/&gt; &lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;200&quot; data-backw=&quot;407&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRk5W568yzge9FZgQeAlwjpkWprrIiagoPSzMm2T2S26RCVT7R6m2BOZA/0?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4914004914004914&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRk5W568yzge9FZgQeAlwjpkWprrIiagoPSzMm2T2S26RCVT7R6m2BOZA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;407&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;可不单老奇葩，新奇葩们似乎也都感到不满哦。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;席瑞暗讽复活投票造假。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;319&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqR6SZgSvQBNlO3ZBz9rWBqprT6erZRjNicx4AgY1OBM1icAoCkrw8LY8Uw/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOzVFFfyMY5PqsNicMEn99icrGwtwvAPQzibgREP71ct9FXpbElicvoNsK4w/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;559.4425087108013&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;329.8954703832752&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqR6SZgSvQBNlO3ZBz9rWBqprT6erZRjNicx4AgY1OBM1icAoCkrw8LY8Uw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5885509838998211&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqR6SZgSvQBNlO3ZBz9rWBqprT6erZRjNicx4AgY1OBM1icAoCkrw8LY8Uw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;559&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;杨奇函意指“很多人都靠剪辑，詹青云是真厉害”。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;150&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRQ8ssrHPGsvMx1r5DplwtMJdbfvKXgwKNg41icEorCOUj1LZu4mfCLbg/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOcTERT3XXC9aFJIwXRmKrhamslmdISB9DjnMibPUiaAI4sY5p333XkMag/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;720&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;203.20557491289196&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;402.64808362369337&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRAPWmAcMUv7uKklU1Kkhn440rMFhSDFEntBfUI6sRZkxpU7tvjlFJjw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.2763888888888889&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRAPWmAcMUv7uKklU1Kkhn440rMFhSDFEntBfUI6sRZkxpU7tvjlFJjw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;720&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;被淘汰的储殷，在微博上感叹“人情凉薄”，又附赠一声呵呵。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;评论区嘉宾纷纷送上拥抱，他独独没有回复许吉如。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;295&quot; data-backw=&quot;500&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRbnKaaMUXicgzrEMjS7FwWhsC9AEibxGxgnfGz9NBckqzpo17lfQRxO5w/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.59&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRbnKaaMUXicgzrEMjS7FwWhsC9AEibxGxgnfGz9NBckqzpo17lfQRxO5w/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;500&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-backh=&quot;669&quot; data-backw=&quot;501&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRlQibd3yjyOjqyKnK5KJgtTnMACWiajD1gT5W0VEMicSYw0Xt9hhlzOUag/?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.3353293413173652&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/icdFiaxvXxvJDY5I79s7eqqadR5CJTcfqRlQibd3yjyOjqyKnK5KJgtTnMACWiajD1gT5W0VEMicSYw0Xt9hhlzOUag/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;501&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;对于许吉如的现场反响不佳，粉丝也能洗——&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;不要高估现场观众的理解能力，观众只喜欢段子。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;但，为什么同样哈佛来的詹青云能夺得满堂彩？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;为什么在胡老师提到婚姻法的时候，自称是律师的许吉如面露尴尬，没有拿起专业知识的武器反驳？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;别太低估观众。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages __bg_gif&quot; data-backh=&quot;302&quot; data-backw=&quot;542&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/icdFiaxvXxvJDDoOrB29ic3t3CZ1tuzIMjOEXFJfqsXofKCCyxz8X82uEX9rRlk7SdN9hCV6Khk4TJ1WpH7TSNRUg/?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5574324324324325&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_g&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
